Package author: Igor Gaponenko

Please describe any modifications that you made to the package in the
reverse time order.

Tag: V00-02-02
2015-08-07 Igor Gaponenko
- automatic authorization for the LDAP management of the instrument groups

Tag: V00-02-01
2014-12-08 Igor Gaponenko
- minor changes in CSS (fonts)

Tag: V00-02-00
2014-04-30 Igor Gaponenko
- moved javascript libraries to package webfwk/

Tag: V00-01-06
2013-08-08 Igor Gaponenko
- changed implementation of html/AuthInstrGroups.php to allow LDAP management
by special instrument science groups and make e-log 'Editor' the standard
privilege for all such groups
- fixed a bug in the AuthDB::hasRole() to deal correctly with POSIX groups

Tag: V00-01-05
2013-05-16 Igor Gaponenko
- rewritten AuthenticationProfile service

Tag: V00-01-04
2013-04-23 Igor Gaponenko
- improved implementation of the authorization script for 'allied' instruments
- reimplemented AuthDB::hasRole() to included POSIX groups in the operation

Tag: V00-01-03
2013-01-28 Igor Gaponenko
- added support for 'allied' instruments in the special group management script AuthInstrGroups.php

Tag: V00-01-00
2012-10-08 Igor Gaponenko
- major code re-organization to separate Web services, JavaScript code and CSS
into dedicated subdirectories

Tag: V00-00-23
2011-11-16 Igor Gaponenko
- migrated from Eclipse to NetBeans IDE

Tag: V00-00-22
2011-09-06 Igor Gaponenko
- added two LDAP tests to cross-check POSIX groups

Tag: V00-00-21
2011-07-07 Igor Gaponenko
- removed unnecessary comments from web/html/LDAP_group_management_log.php
- improved PI search algorithm in web/html/LDAPManagers.php

Tag: V00-00-20
2011-07-01 Igor Gaponenko
- added the MySQL-based logging service. The initial implementation
will only report LDAP group management operations. This will be extended
to cover any operations with AuthDB. 

Tag: V00-00-19
2011-06-30 Igor Gaponenko
- added a new method AuthDB::authRemoteAddr() to report the remote address of a caller
- extended the experiment authorization readyness script to report the number of shifts
- added a new script to report group management operations in LDAP (only when performed via these Web services)

Tag: V00-00-18
2011-06-10 Igor Gaponenko
- fixed a bug in a method fetching privilges from a database

